strategies: It didn't even occur to me that a strategy would be necessary.  Almost all the names corresponded to a real city I knew of.
familiar: Most of the names got a high rating here because I knew of a city with those names.
memorable: Name is unusual or I've personally visited there got higher ratings.
unique: If I was aware of more than one city with that name; I scored it low; otherwise; high.
realistic: Almost every single name corresponded to a city I knew of; so almost every single one got a high rating here.
comments: Not really.  An interesting and different kind of study.  Good luck!
